Definition: synthetic narcotic drug similar to morphine but less habit-forming
Example: used in narcotic detoxification and maintenance of heroin addiction
Synonyms: methadone_hydrochloride, methadon, dolophine_hydrochloride, fixer, synthetic_heroin, narcotic, synthetic, drug, similar, to, morphine, but, less, habit-forming, used, in, detoxification, and, maintenance, of, heroin, addiction
Category: noun.artifact
